-- Brazil Adds 7 Companies to New Auto Regime, O Estado Says
-- B y   M a r i o   S e r g i o   L i m a
-- 2013-01-01T14:20:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-01/brazil-adds-7-companies-to-new-auto-regime-o-estado-says.html
Brazil ’s auto program has established
import quotas for companies without raising taxes, according to
the O Estado de S. Paulo newspaper.  Importers that work with automakers such as South Korean
carmakers  Hyundai Motor Co. (005380)  and  Ssangyong Motor Co. (003620) , and Italy’s
Iveco SpA were among those added to the program, the newspaper
said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
